  Aug. 20, 2025
  
  ![Amanda Norcross](https://www.usnews.com/object/image/00000180-61c1-d187-a5cb-ffdd65070000/amanda-norcross-headshot.jpeg?update-time=1738007708467&size=responsiveSquare300)
  
  ![Leilani Osmundson](https://www.usnews.com/object/image/00000180-61c1-d187-a5cb-ffdd5e690000/headshotsquare.jpg?update-time=&size=responsiveSquare300)
  
  By[Amanda Norcross](https://www.usnews.com/topics/author/amanda-norcross) and [Leilani Osmundson](https://www.usnews.com/topics/author/leilani-osmundson)
  
  \|
  
  Edited by[Zach Watson](https://www.usnews.com/topics/author/zach-watson)
  
  \|
  
  Reviewed by[Erin Evans](https://www.usnews.com/topics/author/erin-evans)
  
