  [26 Top Sonoma Wineries to Visit](https://travel.usnews.com/features/top-sonoma-wineries-to-visit)
  
  ## BaseCamp 37: Kanab, Utah
  
  ![Exterior of illuminated glamping tents at BaseCamp 37 at night.](https://www.usnews.com/object/image/00000198-c2a1-dd48-a19b-e7f154ee0001/credit-basecamp-37.jpg?update-time=1755612009475&size=responsiveFlow640)
  
  Courtesy of BaseCamp 37
  
  For a truly secluded glamping vacation, head to BaseCamp 37, located 40 miles southeast of Zion National Park. Guests enjoy memory foam luxury king-size beds and private decks in each of the five tents available at BaseCamp 37, but what really sets this glampground apart is its [stargazing opportunities](https://travel.usnews.com/features/darkest-skies-in-the-us-for-stargazing). The property is an official "Friend of the Night Sky" and even utilizes unique lighting so guests have the best Milky Way viewing experience.
  
  While you'll need to bring your own groceries or eat at a nearby restaurant, BaseCamp 37 has both outdoor and indoor kitchens for guest use, and provides basic spices, oil and more for cooking. You'll also need to bring your own beverages, though you can store them in the camp's shared refrigerators. Past visitors enjoyed the shared guest lodge and expressed appreciation for the camp hosts.
  
  Address: [5951 E. Eight Mile Gap Road, Kanab, UT 84741](https://www.google.com/maps/place/BaseCamp+37/@37.0044519,-112.3970766,17z/data=!4m22!1m12!3m11!1s0x8734daefe157d797:0x39a716747fcfcd8e!2sBaseCamp+37!5m2!4m1!1i2!8m2!3d37.0044476!4d-112.3945017!9m1!1b1!16s%2Fg%2F11c701b2vz!3m8!1s0x8734daefe157d797:0x39a716747fcfcd8e!5m2!4m1!1i2!8m2!3d37.0044476!4d-112.3945017!16s%2Fg%2F11c701b2vz?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI1MDgwNC4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D)
  
